# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Keep (coordinates,time) in queue and do BFS 

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
collect all rotten apples first with time=0 in queue and change them to taken bt changing their grid[i][j] to 0(suppose)

now start performing BFS by pushing all 4 direction apples which are not rotten and mark them taken by changing their grid[i][j] to 0(suppose)

find maximum value of time and return it
# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(mn)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

